{"tid":691642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔聽阿媽話偷走去游水 巴西少年遭鯊咬噬下體亡","createTime":"2018-06-06T02:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T03:51:46.000Z","uid":158411,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f1b2410b30d438fe1c596eea44f51f35b67d99","tid":691642,"uid":158411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:49:59.000Z","msg":"巴西伯南布哥州累西腓一名18歲少年，周日（3日）無視母親和救生員警告，到一個有鯊魚出沒的海灘游泳，結果陰莖和左方股骨遭鯊魚狂噬，最終失血過多而亡。死者母親收到噩耗後哭成淚人，聞者心酸。<br />\n<br />\n達席爾瓦（Jose Ferreira da Silva）當日下午與兄弟及友人，在當地一個海灘的深水區暢泳。救生員指深水區有鯊魚出沒，着他們返回淺水區，言畢達席爾瓦即遭鯊魚襲擊。由泳客拍攝片段可見，救生員及泳客將他救上岸，傷口不斷滲出血水，場面駭人。<br />\n<br />\n當局表示，達席爾瓦下體及左股骨遭虎鯊噬掉，被送院搶救，最終失血過多不治。其母抵達醫院後痛哭，指曾叮囑兒子不要游泳，後者卻不聽勸告，趁她外出工作時偷偷跑出去，最終賠上性命。在4月，事發海灘一名34歲泳客被鯊魚襲擊，一手一腳被噬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37c941ef29946d7c73717f5d6ad5fb40e54a941","tid":691642,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf50f9b687a47fb2a7de8654ff3a4b979590aa3","tid":691642,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bc2d9147a1d89f5b4c5dd74c2414425416d3d1","tid":691642,"uid":9286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"鯊魚真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7772f72aa1ee42ee5fe43ae5f4eed9eb2462778c","tid":691642,"uid":146604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:40:46.000Z","msg":"好彩冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc9021d5739da454ee382759884129669c88c68","tid":691642,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d916037a04060b5fb9710df5c01e4e260e44bc4b","tid":691642,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da72f06d92006a7d6320dc35f987be5b7837b8a","tid":691642,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7772f72aa1ee42ee5fe43ae5f4eed9eb2462778c","tid":691642,"uid":146604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:40:46.000Z","msg":"好彩冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:47:18.000Z","msg":"你想要咩圖，條魚、個男人定係條野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90f053c248a0b3f92afc8c92d88ad95abc52319","tid":691642,"uid":63414,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8da72f06d92006a7d6320dc35f987be5b7837b8a","tid":691642,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7772f72aa1ee42ee5fe43ae5f4eed9eb2462778c","tid":691642,"uid":146604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:40:46.000Z","msg":"好彩冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:47:18.000Z","msg":"你想要咩圖，條魚、個男人定係條野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:49:04.000Z","msg":"我要晒"},{"pid":"09bbba740987bc86c06d5938ab65bdc9cde1f534","tid":691642,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-